{"text_id":15266,"tokens":["Sto","ichio","metry"," is"," a"," crucial"," aspect"," of"," chemistry"," that"," deals"," with"," the"," quantitative"," relationship"," between"," reactants"," and"," products"," in"," a"," chemical"," reaction","."," It"," helps"," predict"," the"," amount"," of"," product"," that"," can"," be"," formed"," from"," a"," given"," amount"," of"," reactants","."," Learning"," how"," to"," do"," Sto","ichio","metry"," can"," help"," you"," become"," a"," better"," chemist"," and"," enable"," you"," to"," understand"," chemical"," reactions"," quantitatively",".","\n","This"," article"," will"," guide"," you"," through"," the"," steps"," involved"," in"," doing"," Sto","ichio","metry",","," including"," balancing"," equations",","," calculating"," molar"," mass",","," converting"," units",","," and"," determining"," molar"," ratios",".","\n","Part"," ","1",":"," Balancing"," Chemical"," Equations","\n","The"," first"," step"," in"," doing"," Sto","ichio","metry"," is"," to"," balance"," the"," chemical"," equation","."," A"," balanced"," equation"," must"," have"," the"," same"," number"," of"," atoms"," on"," either"," side"," of"," the"," equation","."," Follow"," these"," steps"," to"," balance"," a"," chemical"," equation",":","\n","Write"," down"," the"," equation",":"," Start"," by"," writing"," down"," the"," chemical"," equation"," for"," the"," reaction"," you"," want"," to"," balance",".","\n","Write"," down"," the"," number"," of"," atoms"," that"," comprise"," each"," compound"," on"," either"," side"," of"," the"," equation",":"," Count"," the"," number"," of"," atoms"," of"," each"," element"," on"," both"," sides"," of"," the"," equation"," and"," write"," them"," down","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," determine"," which"," side"," needs"," to"," be"," balanced",".","\n","Add"," a"," coefficient"," in"," front"," of"," elements"," that"," are"," not"," oxygen"," and"," hydrogen"," to"," balance"," each"," side",":"," Begin